issues.description:
In the function `fallback` a non-zero amount of Ether is sent to an address taken from storage slot 1.
There is a check on storage index 1. This storage slot can be written to by calling the function `setup(address)`.
It seems that this function can be called without restrictions.
issues.title: Ether send
